RACE.FOOTNOTES: FINGERS inside rush to the front, maintained command throughout, proving tons best on this day. PINEAPPLE JUICE swiped at the start from the gate, secured the three to the turn, four path in the stretch run while proving no match for the winner. CHOWMEIN no speed to turn, angled out five-six wide into stretch, rallied along for the show spot. SOUTHPOINT unhurried to the turn, rallied along to improve position late for the super spot. TALKSCHEAP inside position with no response when needed in the stretch. CRACK THE MOON tracked three wide to the turn but could not keep up and faded back. DIPLOMATICMAGICIAN had no speed to turn, circled field six-seven wide with no gain in the stretch run. UTOPIAN TREASURE bore out start swiped rival, tried to keep up to the turn but faded back. CLAUDIA'S WILD CAT was through early and dropped back readily. EL MUZN chased winner from two path to the turn but stopped in the stretch.
